然发出爆炸声，3 个窨井盖被炸飞了，满地都是碎片。 记着从旁边美发店店内的监控看到，系一名 10 岁多的小男孩玩叫「电光花」的烟花。 记者来到现场看到，小区物管工作人员正在对被炸飞的窨井盖进行修复。据了解，窨井盖下就是排污管。工作人员介绍，这 3 个窨井盖上都没有开孔，当时孩子只是在上面玩烟花，为什么会引爆被炸飞，着实叫人费解。 随后，民警来到现场，并留下了孩子家长的联系方式。警惕！危险！昆明一小区门口 3 个窨井盖被炸飞！石块飞起五六米… 消防提示：春节临近，孩子燃放烟花爆竹时大人务必到场看护指导，同时一定要远离或避开污水井、化粪池和下水道口，以免引爆沼气造成伤害。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9c22854789f078d9abf1dc6c967fb4f0.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/513316678"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IrvXJsefhh/dREAMaCDc2MzUyMDI2IOrEvo8GMAg4eUAocgk1MTMzMTY2Nzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1643440054.1864603", "card_id": "Q_513379915", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 89}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《开端》的何鹰骏会被如何判刑？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "开端中未对何鹰骏的刑罚做出具体说明，事实上应该如何判刑？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-56f51e4213702aa3f946700e1a161d41_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/513379915"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrvXJsefhh/dREAMaCDc2MzY2MDM2IPyVwI8GMA84wgFAKXIJNTEzMzc5OTE1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1643440054.186822", "card_id": "Q_511481597", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 344}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "初二成绩好几科不及格，现在学还能考上高中吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今天出分了，数学 10 分，我怕我考不上高中，现在学还来得及吗，理科严重不好，说什么都可以，我能承担起"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-57233720f3b7f8013248fa9cd0095e8f_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/511481597"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrvXJsefhh/dREAMaCDc1OTQ0MTUzIJzjg48GMBM4jANAKnIJNTExNDgxNTk3eACqAQ